  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a 1-year, multicenter, Phase 2, open-label safety study in subjects with unilateral
      Meniere's disease. Subjects will receive 1 intratympanic (IT) injection of 12 mg OTO-104 at
      3-month intervals for a total of 4 injections total.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
